---
title: HelloHero: Double Creamy Chicken Spaghetti with Tomato & Parsley
description: Golden ropes of spaghetti coated in a rich, creamy tomato sauce and tender chunks of chicken sounds like an ideal meal to us. Finished with a pinch of chilli flakes if you like a bit of heat, this is nothing short of a small bite of heaven.

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/65813c8234da163846f083cb-9f1c82d0.jpeg
